nodes.text: An unidentified Zabrak was a member of the Nightbrothers during the Clone Wars.

This Zabrak was one of the many brought forward by Brother Viscus to appear in front of Asajj Ventress for her selection of capable potential candidates to aid in her plan to get revenge against Count Dooku. This Zabrak was eliminated because Ventress believed he was too weak so she punched him to the ground.
